headline: Henry Schein Will Showcase a Selection of the Company’s Comprehensive Solutions for Oral Health Professionals at the 2025 International Dental Show
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., March 25, 2025--Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC) will showcase a selection of its comprehensive business and practice solutions, and provide perspectives on the future of dentistry, during the 2025 International Dental Show (IDS) in Cologne, Germany, from March 25 to 29, 2025, at the Koelnmesse in Hall 4.1, Stand A-090 and A-008.
